Package: devid-schema
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Multi-Arch: foreign
Suggests: slapd
Description: LDAP schema file for devid device management schema
 The devid schema allow the association between hardware devices
 through its serial number and an existing LDAP user.
 Using this schema, it is possible to restrict local hotplugable
 devices such as USB devices only to those allowed for the locally
 connected user.

